description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Introduction:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Circle Integrated Care is looking for an enthusiastic advanced practice physiotherapist to become part of the MSK team in Greenwich. The role is unique and may include working in a clinical GP setting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting opportunity to work in a dynamic Integrated Care Service with a full musculoskeletal multi-disciplinary team.  The post holder will be expected to provide clinical expertise, leadership and collaborate with all other clinicians working alongside them, becoming part of an MDT approach to enhance patient care in a musculoskeletal setting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post would suit an experienced MSK physiotherapist looking to expand on their clinical skills. This would suit an experienced band 8a equivalent.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mentorship will be provided by experienced APP and our clinical training academy. Travel between Greenwich sites may be required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role &amp; Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This APP position is a key role within Circle Integrated Care services in Greenwich.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The summary for this role is:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To be one of the senior clinician’s representing Circle Integrated Care in the Greenwich hub and in GP settings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To participate when needed in triaging, SDM and physio line models for other Circle sites.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Person Specification:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;HCPC registered&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Physiotherapy degree&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working at a senior physiotherapist level seeing patients in a musculoskeletal setting (equivalent 8a)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evidence of continuing professional development in relevant clinical and management areas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clinical leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in ordering diagnostics/investigations &amp; tests&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience of clinical supervision / mentoring&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in Orthopaedics, Rheumatology and Chronic pain&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;27 days’ annual leave pro rata with additional days for long-term service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cycle to work scheme: save money on a new bike and benefit from interest-free instalments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Private pension scheme helping your to live well in retirement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Health and wellbeing programme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employee assistance programme: get confidential support 24/7&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Private medical insurance to help you get any treatment you need quickly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Non-contributory life assurance and income protection insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Childcare vouchers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Season ticket loan: get the benefit of an annual ticket and pay the cost over 12 months&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
